{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamref\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE5write6buffer5count11cancellableSiSvSg_SiAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO15OutputStreamRefV","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","extendedModule":"GIO","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"write","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to write "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" into the stream. Will block"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"during the operation.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamRef\/OutputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamRef\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"write"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"!, "},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If count is 0, returns 0 and does nothing. A value of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"larger than "},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will cause a "},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", then the operation can be cancelled by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is set accordingly.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStreamRef/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)":{"abstract":[{"text":"Tries to write ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" into the stream. Will block"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"during the operation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamref\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamRef\/write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","title":"write(buffer:count:cancellable:)","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"write","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"buffer"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"